  "response": "As of 2023, one of the best Android phones above \u20b935,000 is the Samsung Galaxy S23. Here are some of its key features:\n\n- **Display**: 6.1-inch Dynamic AMOLED 2X, 120Hz refresh rate\n- **Processor**: Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 2\n- **RAM**: 8GB\n- **Storage**: 128GB/256GB\n- **Camera**: \n  - Rear: 50MP wide, 12MP ultra-wide, 10MP telephoto\n  - Front: 12MP\n- **Battery**: 3,900mAh with 25W fast charging\n- **Operating System**: Android 13 with One UI 5.1\n\nOther strong contenders in this price range include:\n\n1. **OnePlus 11**:\n   - **Display**: 6.7-inch AMOLED, 120Hz refresh rate\n   - **Processor**: Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 2\n   - **RAM**: 8GB/16GB\n   - **Storage**: 128GB/256GB\n   - **Camera**: \n     - Rear: 50MP wide, 48MP ultra-wide, 32MP telephoto\n     - Front: 16MP\n   - **Battery**: 5,000mAh with 80W fast charging\n   - **Operating System**: Android 13 with OxygenOS 13\n\n2. **Google Pixel 7 Pro**:\n   - **Display**: 6.7-inch LTPO AMOLED, 120Hz refresh rate\n   - **Processor**: Google Tensor G2\n   - **RAM**: 12GB\n   - **Storage**: 128GB/256GB/512GB\n   - **Camera**: \n     - Rear: 50MP wide, 12MP ultra-wide, 48MP telephoto\n     - Front: 10.8MP\n   - **Battery**: 5,000mAh with 23W fast charging\n   - **Operating System**: Android 13\n\nThese phones offer excellent performance, high-quality cameras, and robust software support, making them top choices in the premium Android market segment.",
